desc: Reclamation is a boutique store located in Portland, Oregon. With a passion for trinkets and oddities, it boasts a large collection of curated art, ceramics, plants as well as bath and body goods.

layout.text: Reclamation is a woman of color-owned boutique shop located in Portland, OR that features handmade goods, plants, gifts, and terrariums, as well as our own handmade line of goods.
